'''摩爾門帶'''（Mormon Corridor）是指北美西部在1850年至約1890年期間[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]成員（即摩爾門教徒）聚居的一個地區<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nps.gov/nr/twhp/wwwlps/lessons/122fort/122facts1.htm |title=Origin of the term from a part of the National Park Service's "The Old Mormon Fort: Birthplace of Las Vegas, Nevada" |access-date=2016-07-17 |archive-date=2017-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515021814/https://www.nps.gov/nr/twhp/wwwlps/lessons/122fort/122facts1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在學術領域，這一地區又稱摩爾門文化區<ref>[http://www.juvenileinstructor.org/the-current-state-of-the-mormon-culture-region/ The Current State of the Mormon Culture Region] {{Wayback|url=http://www.juvenileinstructor.org/the-current-state-of-the-mormon-culture-region/ |date=20171115215615 }} This reference also includes a map, by county of Leading Church Bodies from 2000</ref><ref>{{cite book |title= Transformation of the Mormon Culture Region |first= Ethan R. |last= Yorgason |publisher= [[University_of_Illinois_Press|University of Illinois Press]] |year= 2003 |isbn= 978-0-252-02853-3 }} ([https://books.google.com/books?id=-ewPkecIv8cC&dq=%22Mormon+culture+region%22&printsec=frontcover&source=bl&ots=XL7c5hrTzM&sig=_vw-OUTLKkQ8lBtQ4COE1j3XRAs&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=18&ct=result Selected text] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-ewPkecIv8cC&dq=%22Mormon+culture+region%22&printsec=frontcover&source=bl&ots=XL7c5hrTzM&sig=_vw-OUTLKkQ8lBtQ4COE1j3XRAs&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=18&ct=result |date=20210323041432 }})</ref>。和美國東南部的[[聖經帶|聖經帶]]相對，這一地區因[[摩爾門經|摩爾門經]]而又被稱為「摩爾門經帶」。摩爾門地帶的中心是[[猶他州|猶他州]]，同時也包括了[[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]]、[[懷俄明州|懷俄明州]]、[[內華達州|內華達州]]、[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]的部分地區。由於摩爾門地帶的中心城市[[鹽湖城|鹽湖城]]的[[Jell-O|Jell-O]]（一種果凍類甜點）銷量很高，這一地區又稱Jell-O帶。

